snippet.title: Wakey Wakey | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist & Follow: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3047720/Wakey_Wakey/

Wakey Wakey is a Puzzle Platformer with a unique world-bending twist. Navigate your everchanging bedroom, take control of new household objects, and overcome surprising obstacles to help this sleepy guy get a good night's rest. Grab your favorite teddy bear and put on your pajamas! Navigate your everchanging bedroom, with Moon Jam Games LLC & VoxPop Games, Inc.

It's late at night and you wake up to find yourself laying down on the floor. Somehow you must have rolled out of bed. Better walk across your room so you can get some sleep. Just when you're about to drift off, you open your eyes to find yourself on the floor again, but something seems... different.

Follow our Socials for more updates!
